182, 167.0225, 167.8196, 168.3566, 167.5826, 166.17, 165.4985, 165.5599, 165.2532, 165.3864, 165.246, 164.8222, 165.7045, 164.9384, 165.0213, 166.0242, 166.2679, 167.3361, 168.0522, 168.0526, 167.479, 168.0113, 167.9524, 168.1028, 168.6951, 169.3391, 169.1515, 168.9648, 168.2565, 166.0768, 167.2052, 167.5925, 167.0551, 167.0892, 166.7264, 165.0375, 165.5497, 165.7737, 166.6815, 166.0723, 165.7366, 165.9068, 165.5634, 166.3195, 167.507, 168.0029, 168.1075, 168.0643, 167.582, 166.4273, 165.9452, 166.0657, 165.0218, 164.7345, 165.3348, 165.7014, 166.4987, 166.9266, 167.0912, 167.1398, 168.2032, 166.7682, 167.2723, 167.2084, 168.0139, 167.9039, 167.4837, 167.1407, 166.6908, 166.8061, 168.1088, 168.3688, 167.6562, 168.5068, 169.1649, 169.9303, 169.5914, 169.9869, 169.6674, 169.46, 169.3065, 169.2345, 169.1805, 168.9698, 168.6253, 168.259, 168.7922, 168.6208, 169.2699, 169.2438, 168.6618, 169.6599, 170.2953, 170.5058, 170.0595, 169.231, 169.3354, 168.2468, 168.718, 170.5417, 169.9891, 169.1889, 170.1431, 170.6011, 170.8396, 170.12, 170.0265, 171.1174, 169.9118, 168.5227, 168.7531, 168.666, 168.8017, 170.7769, 170.0479, 170.1888, 170.5019, 170.8268, 173.4535, 173.9496, 173.6727, 172.2155, 174.3901, 175.2121, 175.392, 176.3728, 176.4374, 173.8734, 173.8728, 172.9553, 174.6837, 175.1232, 174.5422, 175.0817, 176.3128, 176.2187, 176.2624, 176.6075, 177.1948, 178.1231, 179.4641, 181.5916, 182.1417, 183.3907, 181.7018, 181.8262, 182.5207, 183.8921, 182.0535, 183.106, 181.7038, 181.3224, 181.7801, 182.1751, 180.7513, 178.4628, 176.258, 177.5916, 176.6234, 178.1591, 178.8736, 179.351, 180.3126, 177.9486], "summary_html": "<h1>沪铜多因子 -- 通过 (Sharpe 1.08)</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>研报以沪铜为例，从宏观、库存、利润、升贴水四大类约100个指标中筛选出23个因子（Sharpe&gt;0.5且胜率&gt;45%），对每个指标分别采用动量/单均线/双均线/历史分位数策略构建交易信号。同类因子等权叠加仓位形成子策略，子策略间再等权叠加得到多因子组合。本复现将原文沪铜单品种方法推广至全品种截面，使用日频数据中的真实基本面字段（ry/basis/profit/inventory_21/receipt）替代原文外部数据源，构建四类截面因子（carry/库存/基差/利润），截面排名后等权组合形成多因子仓位。</p>\n<p>核心逻辑：基本面因子在品种截面上具有预测力（CS IC = 0.019），多因子组合通过分散化降低回撤并提升风险调整收益。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>1.02</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>5.6%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>5.4%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-12.9%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.04</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3450</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.13</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>1.07</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.4 / 0.94</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2012</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>1.23</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.18</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.14</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.66</span></td><td>0.62</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.53</span></td><td>0.9</td><td>1.05</td><td>1.71</td><td>1.26</td><td>1.65</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.34</span></td><td>0.43</td><td>0.42</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">4.17</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>ry</code></td><td>展期收益</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>basis</code></td><td>基差</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>inventory_21</code></td><td>库存(21日)</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>receipt</code></td><td>仓单</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>profit</code></td><td>利润</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 10 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 10 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3452</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>99.2%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>39.6</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p><strong>Carry因子</strong>（使用展期收益ry）:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{carry}_N^{(i,t)} = \\frac{1}{N} \\sum_{k=0}^{N-1} \\text{ry}^{(i, t-k)}, \\quad N \\in \\{20, 40, 60, 80, 120\\}</div>\n<p><strong>库存因子</strong>（inventory_21 + receipt动量，方向反转）:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{inv}_N^{(i,t)} = -\\left(\\frac{\\text{inventory\\_21}^{(i,t)}}{\\text{inventory\\_21}^{(i,t-N)}} - 1\\right), \\quad N \\in \\{20, 40, 60\\}</div>\n<p><strong>基差因子</strong>（basis水平 + 双均线差值）:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{basis\\_lvl}_N^{(i,t)} = \\text{MA}_N(\\text{basis}^{(i)}), \\quad \\text{basis\\_dma}_{s,l}^{(i,t)} = \\text{MA}_s(\\text{basis}^{(i)}) - \\text{MA}_l(\\text{basis}^{(i)})</div>\n<p><strong>利润因子</strong>（动量，方向反转）:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{profit}_N^{(i,t)} = -\\left(\\frac{\\text{profit}^{(i,t)}}{\\text{profit}^{(i,t-N)}} - 1\\right), \\quad N \\in \\{20, 40, 60\\}</div>\n<p><strong>组合</strong>：各因子截面排名 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\to</span> 同类因子等权平均 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\to</span> 子策略等权叠加 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\to</span> <code>rank_to_continuous(scale=2.0)</code> 映射到 <span class=\"math-tex\">[-1, 1]</span> <span class=\"math-tex\">\\to</span> <code>rebalance_hold</code> 每H天换仓。</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>Sharpe 0.991, 换手 0.536, 12变体</td><td>基线: carry(5窗口)+inv(3窗口)+basis(4窗口)+profit(2窗口), 截面排名等权组合, hold grid 5-20天</td><td>f4_h10=0.991 通过阈值</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>换手偏高, f4_h15接近f4_h10, 2016/2023年Sharpe弱</td><td>加长basis/profit窗口(+60), 扩展hold grid(h10/15/20), 加vol_target变体</td><td>Sharpe 0.991-&gt;1.077, 换手从0.536降至0.464</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>R2最优稳定, IC gate对截面因子无效</td><td>精简变体, 加f4_h12, 加IC-gate和vt多组合</td><td>Sharpe稳定1.077, IC gate反降至0.59(截面非时序), skip</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折</strong>: R2 增加 profit_60 和 basis_lvl_60/basis_dma_20_60 更长窗口使 4-factor 组合 Sharpe 从 0.99 提升至 1.08。IC gate 在 R3 反而降低了 Sharpe（从 1.08 降至 0.59），因为该因子的 alpha 来源是截面排名而非品种内时序预测（TS IC = 0.003 接近零）。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种（58个），盈利集中在 J, V, JM, P, I（黑色+化工）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 10-15 天</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 时序 IC 接近 0（0.003），信号完全依赖截面排名，品种内无预测力\n<p>- 2016 年和 2023 年 Sharpe 接近 0，策略在某些宏观环境下失效 - 与因子库中 <code>gtja_bi_basis_ma20_60_H15_cs</code> 相关性 0.67（likely_redundant），但 Sharpe 低于该因子（1.08 vs 1.41） - 基本面字段非空率 20-45%，部分品种/日期缺失导致因子覆盖度有限 - 原文Sharpe 2.05针对沪铜单品种，全品种截面化后因非目标品种稀释而下降</p>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 0.995</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.86s</li>\n</ul>"}